  <h3 class="group-title" id="territorial-offices">Territorial offices</h3>
    
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>The territorial offices have summarised their priorities for this Parliament.</p>
</div>
</div>


