  <h3 class="group-title" id="sustainable-development-goals">Sustainable development goals</h3>
    
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>The UK is committed to the delivery of the Sustainable Development Goals. It does this by ensuring that the goals are embedded in departments’ plans.</p>
</div>
</div>


